### Incident Header Branding

#### [MODIFY] [CrisisCard.tsx](file:///c:/Users/ahash/Downloads/crio-research-v/crisis_nexus_ngo/components/CrisisCard.tsx)
* **Capitalized Header Cleanup:** Update the incident `eventName` resolution logic to filter out `"unknown"` subtype values and use the clean capitalized fallback pattern established in the map layer banner:
  ```typescript
  const eventName = (
    crisis.title || 
    (crisis.subType && crisis.subType !== "unknown" ? crisis.subType : null) || 
    crisis.eventType || 
    "CRITICAL INCIDENT"
  ).toUpperCase();
  ```

