### Telemetry Safety Layer

#### [MODIFY] [DataQualityLayer.tsx](file:///c:/Users/ahash/Downloads/crio-research-v/crisis_nexus_ngo/components/DataQualityLayer.tsx)
* **Refactor Degradation Heuristic:** Update `sourceMode` logic to ensure mobile origin alone is not flagged as degraded. Only mark as `MOBILE_DEGRADED` if the telemetry coordinates are missing or stale:
  ```typescript
  const isMobileSource = item.client === 'mobile' || item.source === 'mobile' || item.isMobileDegraded;
  const isMissingLocation = !item.location?.lat && type !== 'user' && type !== 'intelligence';
  const isStaleLocation = item.stale;
  
  if (isMobileSource && (isMissingLocation || isStaleLocation)) {
    sourceMode = "MOBILE_DEGRADED";
  }
  ```

